    <p class="event-description">Our first event will be a collection mode tournament.</p>
    <p class="event-description">Collection mode is a game mode built into Mul-Ty-Player where points are awarded for each item collected.</p>
    <p class="event-description">For this event, you will all be split into groups of 3 based on skill level and availability. At the start of the session, you will all choose a level to run through. You will then have 5 minutes to run through the level together and collect as much as possible. Collectibles are synchronised so when someone collects something, no one else can get it. Your goal is to collect the most. At the end of the 3 minutes, your points will be noted down and the next player’s level will be run.</p>
    <p class="event-description">After all three rounds, your total score will dictate your placement.</p>
    <p class="event-description">You will be awarded 3 points for first, 2 for second and 1 for third.</p>
