    <h1 class="event-title">THE WEAKEST SKINK - SATURDAY 3RD AUGUST</h1>
    <p class="event-info">Estimated Session Length: 1.5 Hours</p>
    <p class="event-description">The weakest link is a British game show in which contestants answer a series of questions. Each question must be answered within 10 seconds. The original show also had a banking system for the players to make money but this will not be a part of the event. The first round lasts 3 minutes with each subsequent round being 10 seconds shorter. After each round all players vote for who they believe the weakest player is. That player is then removed from the game and the game continues. Once there are only 2 players remaining, 3 questions are asked to each player alternating each time until one player has answered more than the other correctly. In the event of a tie, a sudden death back and forth questioning begins.</p>
    <p class="event-description">2 points will go to the first player out 3 to the winner 2 to second place and 1 to the last player voted out.</p>
    <p class="event-description">I advise you to watch the show to better understand the format before the event.</p>
