    <p class="event-description">Chaos mode is a pseudo randomizer built into Mul-Ty-Player which shuffles the positions of all cogs across 50 positions and all bilbies across 25 positions in each level.</p>
    <p class="event-description">All portals to the 9 main stages are also shuffled so no one will know which order they’ll be completing the levels.</p>
    <p class="event-description">In this event, you’ll be working with a partner to try to beat the opposing team to collect all golden cogs and all bilbies in a level shuffled with chaos mode. Opals and Thunder Eggs are not required. The event will be run in a best of three rounds. The first team to win two rounds wins. Levels will be decided using the first three level portals in the game which will be randomly shuffled using chaos mode. The seed will be pre-determined and the same for both teams.</p>
